    <div class="news-card" date="1536593124090">
      <p><b>SEP 10</b></p>
      <p>Support for RTL Languages, Account Preferences and more!</p>
      <br>
      <p><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-paragraph"></i></span> RTL Languages</p>
      <p>As promised, Cryptee Docs now supports right-to-left languages. You can even mix left-to-right text alongside right-to-left. And if you commonly use RTL languages, you can set this as your default in your Account Preferences.</p>
      <br>
      <p><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-sliders"></i></span> Account Preferences</p>
      <p>You can now adjust and set your preferences, and they will sync across all your devices. Starting with two preferences, and more on the way.</p><br>
      <p>First is Inactivity Timeout in minutes. You can now set Cryptee to automatically forget your key and lock things down after some minutes of inactivity.</p><br>
      <p>Second is Text & Language Direction. If you commonly use right-to-left languages, you can set it as your default for Cryptee Docs, and all your new documents will use RTL.</p><br>
      <p><span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-flask"></i></span> Public Beta Platform</p>
      <p>Public Beta testing platform is almost complete! There are some amazing new features on the horizon, like batch imports from other applications, speed optimizations, design &amp; usability updates, dark mode and more! If you're interested in beta testing some of these, please reach out via <i>info [at] crypt {dot} ee</i>.</p>
    </div>

