    <div class="news-card" date="1533809256983">
      <p><b>AUG 09</b></p>
      <p>Archived Folders for Cryptee Docs</p><br>
      <p>Introducing another highly requested feature, "Archived Folders". If you have lots of folders full of docs and would like to get rid of the visual clutter, you can now archive your folders in Cryptee Docs.</p><br>
      <p>To do so, click &nbsp; <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-archive"></i></span><i>Archive Folder</i> &nbsp; from the folder's dropdown.</p>
      <p>They will be hidden below all your folders, and you can easily un-archive them by clicking the <span class="icon"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-recycle"></i></span> button.</p>
    </div>

